,{"pid":"e8b26d9d61cfa8b78969d88a3e316bad2967676e","tid":8243,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T22:20:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇鼓底 好難挽cajon挽得叻<br />\n鼓易過Cajon 多聲多配搭好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀 冇鼓底未必夠力挽cajon<br />\n始終有一定重量！"},{"pid":"da36450415baa17b997bc4506b42028a3bee5c1b","tid":8243,"uid":15938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T22:27:37.000Z","msg":"挽你老母<br />\n冇力挽就練大隻d"},{"pid":"d60cf381018f2af0b002c9f7584123a27b537fc6","tid":8243,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T22:33:21.000Z","msg":"咩都唔識就咁學 其實都難試上手 <br />\n<br />\nD 線按到手指痛"},{"pid":"dba9dd07ef10d544432607a56b0e793aba23a200","tid":8243,"uid":36165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"Ukulele玩得勁可以好正，同結他係完全兩個feel。但而家d人學ukulele都係for fun,貪佢細細個，禁線又唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c02ca64cf8442e3d993d4c8c8919a3373fdfb5","tid":8243,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ukulele玩得勁可以好正，同結他係完全兩個feel。但而家d人學ukulele都係for fun,貪佢細細個，禁線又唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知ukulele 可以好有自己風格同玩得好勁，不過好似好多人多貪佢比結他易學同携帶先玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12e99d5fe238b803521804cf6d174c575ce0ad4","tid":8243,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"ukulele 好難聽<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解d人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e571276b7f9e18233c7c527cc16cce9af0361f7","tid":8243,"uid":36165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:13:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ukulele 好難聽<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解d人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nukulele如果淨係聽d低技巧型既歌係好悶，可以試下聽d大師彈ukulele,一定會顛覆你對佢既印象，例如jake shimabukuro既while my guitar gently weeps同Dragon"},{"pid":"5b7f408f590c23065803afa959ea1da97361eadb","tid":8243,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ukulele 好難聽<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解d人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nukulele如果淨係聽d低技巧型既歌係好悶，可以試下聽d大師彈ukulele,一定會顛覆你對佢既印象，例如jake shimabukuro既while my guitar gently weeps同Dragon</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f397c4ed2fe3b3a83dff12eb5ea8c334952526f","tid":8243,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇鼓底 好難挽cajon挽得叻<br />\n鼓易過Cajon 多聲多配搭好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鼓點見得易過Cajon?<br />\n如果你話由零學 鼓係講四肢 cajon你可以兩隻手基本上玩到好多野<br />\n利申:識打鼓但玩cajon多"},{"pid":"8eb729c1868092d35e29eb4001b7ced076a1ecd2","tid":8243,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇鼓底 好難挽cajon挽得叻<br />\n鼓易過Cajon 多聲多配搭好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鼓點見得易過Cajon?<br />\n如果你話由零學 鼓係講四肢 cajon你可以兩隻手基本上玩到好多野<br />\n利申:識打鼓但玩cajon多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而調返轉講亦唔見得cajon易過full set好多<br />\n講入門一定cajon易入d但係對自已有要求要玩上去既話 cajon都有full set無既元素係入面"}]}